    <item>
      <title>拜登劝阻以色列不要袭击伊朗油田</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/biden-discourages-israel-from-attacking-iran-s-oil-fields</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登试图阻止以色列袭击伊朗油田，而美国则希望影响总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡对弹道导弹袭击的反应，并防止该地区陷入全面战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/biden-discourages-israel-from-attacking-iran-s-oil-fields</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 18:30:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布鲁塞尔因绿色议程受阻推迟实施柴油限排政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/brussels-to-delay-diesel-limits-amid-pushback-on-green-agenda</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于气候措施遭到广泛反对，布鲁塞尔推迟了禁止大量柴油汽车进入欧盟首都的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/brussels-to-delay-diesel-limits-amid-pushback-on-green-agenda</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 17:47:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东冲突加剧暴露美国对以色列影响力的局限性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-10-04/us-limited-leverage-with-israel-shows-as-mideast-conflict-widens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡正在升级与伊朗的斗争。距离美国总统大选还有一个月的时间，拜登政府无法——也不会——阻止他。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-10-04/us-limited-leverage-with-israel-shows-as-mideast-conflict-widens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 16:00:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟通过新一轮电动汽车关税战测试其对抗中国的能力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/eu-tests-its-mettle-to-take-on-china-with-new-ev-tariff-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟对中国动用了其最有力的经济工具之一，对电动汽车征收关税，此举增加了中国采取报复措施以及对国内消费者和企业产生不利影响的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/eu-tests-its-mettle-to-take-on-china-with-new-ev-tariff-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 15:33:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
